msgid ""
"Given a classification, a combination of algorithm rasters can be "
"produced, in order to create a raster with the lowest \"distances\" (i.e."
" pixels have the value of the algorithm raster corresponding to the class"
" they belong in the classification). Therefore, this raster can be useful"
" to identify pixels that require the collection of more similar spectral "
"signatures (see :ref:`classification_preview`)."
msgstr ""

