msgstr ""

#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:751
msgid ""
"Jeffries-Matusita Distance calculates the separability of a pair of "
"probability distributions. This can be particularly meaningful for "
"evaluating the results of :ref:`max_likelihood_algorithm` "
"classifications."
msgstr ""

#: ../../remote_sensing.rst:754
msgid ""
"The Jeffries-Matusita Distance :math:`J_{xy}` is calculated as (Richards "
